dct_title_s: Map Israel's national parks / produced and published by the Survey of Israel.; National Parks Authority. (Text)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Depth shown by isolines. Ancillary map: The Middle East. Maps shows cease fireline 1967, disengagement line 1974, ruins/antiquity sites,  ancient synagogues, churches or monasteries, mosques, roads, and railroads. "This map is not an authority on boundaries." Descriptions of each site on verso. © Copyrigh reserved by the Survey of Israel.
dct_publisher_sm: a Tel Aviv : Survey of Israel, 1993.
